getProperty

public String getProperty(String propertyName)
Description copied from interface: PropertiesResolver
Returns a property from the map. If a property does not exist null will be returned. The returned property value will have had its value resolved of any placeholders (variables i.e. ${xxx}). They will only remain if they failed to resolve.
